{"type":null,"faqId":49816,"title":"手机指示灯颜色有什么含义？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body4564592\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__p36524737\">手机状态指示灯能反映电池电量状态提示或事件提示。</p><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__ul60287183\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__li41081332\">红色闪烁：电池电量低、电池过放无法充电或不能正常开机。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__li34187673\">红色长亮（充电状态下）：电池电量低于警戒值。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__li39253609\">橙色长亮（充电状态下）：电池电量高于警戒值。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__li17738163\">绿色长亮（充电状态下）：充电接近完成或已经完成。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__li25425746\">绿色闪烁：有新消息、新邮件、未接来电、日程提醒，或错过的闹钟。</li></ul><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__note5713736\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79d70_ov1rk.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p class=\"text\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264500__p27505126\">部分第三方应用，比如 QQ、微博、微信等，如有新通知，指示灯也可能会显示为绿色闪烁或蓝色闪烁。</p></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264500","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615544000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":56,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"指示灯","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}